<inglise> REGULATION (EEC) No 1375/75 OF THE COMMISSION of 29 May 1975 on the provisions of recognition of producer groups for hops in Ireland </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 1375/75 humalasektori tootjar&uuml;hmade tunnustamise kohta Iirimaal 29. mai 1975 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 1696/71 (1) of 26 July 1971 on the common organization of the market in hops, as amended by the Act (2) concerning the conditions of accession and the adjustments to the Treaties, and in particular Article 7 (5) thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 26. juuli 1971. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1696/71 humalaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) muudetud &uuml;hinemistingimusi ja asutamislepingutesse tehtavaid muudatusi k&auml;sitleva aktiga, (2) eriti selle artikli 7 l&otilde;iget 5, ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Commission Regulation (EEC) No 1351/72 (3) of 28 June 1972 on the recognition of producer groups for hops, provides in Article 2 (1) that for purposes of recognition a producer group must consist of at least seven producers; </inglise>
<eesti> komisjoni 28. juuni 1972. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1351/73 (tootjar&uuml;hmade tunnustamise kohta humalasektoris (3)) artikli 2 l&otilde;ikega 1 n&auml;hakse ette, et tunnustuse saamiseks peab tootjar&uuml;hmal olema v&auml;hemalt seitse liiget; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas since the entry into force of this Regulation Community rules on agriculture have become applicable to Ireland; </inglise>
<eesti> alates selle m&auml;&auml;ruse j&otilde;ustumisest kohaldatakse Iirimaa suhtes &uuml;henduse p&otilde;llumajanduseeskirju; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas in that country there is only one hop producing region and whereas that region contains less than seven producers; </inglise>
<eesti> k&otilde;nealuses riigis on vaid &uuml;ks humalakasvatuspiirkond ja selles piirkonnas on alla seitsme tootja; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas because of Ireland's geographical situation it would be difficult for Irish producers to join producer groups in other Member States; whereas the producers in question, four in number, otherwise fulfil all the conditions required by Regulation (EEC) No 1351/72 for the formation of a recognized producer group; </inglise>
<eesti> Iirimaa geograafilise asendi t&otilde;ttu on Iirimaa toojatel raske &uuml;hineda teiste liikmesriikide toojar&uuml;hmadega; k&otilde;nealused 4 tootjat vastavad k&otilde;ikidele teistele m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 1351/72 toojar&uuml;hmade tunnustamiseks kehtestatud tingimustele; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas in order not to create a situation liable to prejudice these producers in relation to other producers in the Community it is necessary to derogate from the provisions of Article 2 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 1351/72 in favour of Ireland by reducing to three the minimum number of producers required for the formation of a group; </inglise>
<eesti> ei tekiks olukord, kus need tootjad on v&otilde;rreldes &uuml;henduse teiste tootjatega ebasoodsamas olukorras, on vaja Iirimaa puhul kehtestada erand m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1351/72 artikli 2 l&otilde;ikest 1, v&auml;hendades tootjar&uuml;hma loomiseks n&otilde;utut liikmete arvu kolmeni; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the Opinion of the Management Committee for Hops, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses s&auml;testatud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las humalaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> In Ireland, in derogation from Article 2 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 1351/72, a group of producers may be recognized if it is composed of at least three producers. </inglise>
<eesti> Erandina m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1351/72 artikli 2 l&otilde;ikest 1 v&otilde;ib Iirimaal tunnustada tootjar&uuml;hmi, millel on v&auml;hemalt kolm liiget. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the third day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub kolmandal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 29 May 1975. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 29. mai 1975 </eesti>
